# =============================================================================
# STORAGE & STABILITY
# =============================================================================
STORAGE:
  - Store in cool, dry place (secure configuration repository)
  - Keep container tightly closed (access-controlled)
  - Protect from extreme heat (thermal throttling attacks)
  - Use within 2 years of opening (security updates expire)
  - Discard if color/texture changes (compromise detected)

STABILITY:
  - Shelf Life: 3 years unopened
  - After Opening: 2 years with regular updates
  - Degradation: 10% effectiveness loss per year
  - Refresh: Apply security patches monthly
  - Replacement: Major version upgrade annually

